5. THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

   This Platform uses open-source libraries (React, Pixi.js, Howler.js,
   Zustand, PostHog, and others). Those libraries retain their original
   licences and are not affected by this document. See package.json for
   the full dependency list.

